> Hello Guys and Gals,
> I seem to have a few clamps that resemble a spade or a diamond or even a
> heart shaped top.  The camp appears to be solid.
> I have mangled two now in getting  the fuel lines replaced.
> Any helpful hints to removing these before I hurt something?
